shortcode_media.title: A New Dawn: journey of children with special needs through this pandemic

node.text:
.
Clueless about the pandemic,  children with special needs struggled a lot without the teachers that guide and provide an accommodating and learning environment.

@prabhat_education_foundation , an Ahmedabad-based NGO that works with children with disabilities, supported them through online classes and therapy.

But going back to the new normal would require funds so that new and safe educational material at the centre along with food kits can be arranged for Prabhat's students.

Help Prabhat in raising funds for the children who can have a better future through appropriate education. 
Donate using UPI Id/QR code/Bank details. Details mentioned in Link in Bio.

The UPI Id is: Paytmqr2810050501011013bp2341nr@paytm (works for all online payment platforms). 

While using the QR code, it's advisable to take screenshot of the QR code and then scan from the gallery. 
For bank details, refer the link in bio.

For any query, please feel free to contact at : prabhat@prabhatedu.org

With or without a photo this will forever be embedded into my memories. I still love California but with love comes the good and the bad days. How you carry yourself is how you get through those dark ones. See this photo reminds me of how bad it really can be. So, with that being said those bright and sunny days are even more beautiful to you. Because you know you have already lived through the worst of times. To strive is one of the best remedies to a lifetime of healing. So, 2020 you will not get the best of me. I will see you in my rearview as time passes by. I am stronger. I am going to keep on smiling even on those darker days! ❤️☺️

If you can relate let’s show 2020 we are stronger than any virus or any catastrophic wildfire. 🔥 😷 🦠
